---
title: Meatballs in Caramelized Onion Gravy with German-Style Apple-Potato Mash
description: Caramelizing turns the humble onion into an addictively savoury-sweet treat. Make it into a gravy, and you have a simple, flavourful sauce that will have everyone licking their plates clean! This sauce shines poured over subtly sweet apple mashed potatoes and mustardy beef meatballs.
